{"id": "1431026305855655936", "channel_id": "1431009422020186142", "type": 19, "author_id": "201897606572539904", "author_name": "hitsu4", "author_bot": false, "content": "If you are looking purely from a meta standpoint, pulling now for Castor or in a few weeks for Tawil would be the better option. If you like Pollux cause you like Pollux, then grab him. If you want to go the middle route, grab the brothers (Castor and Pollux) since they do synergize well,  however just Castor really does fine without Pollux.  For standard it will depend on what unit you decide to pull for, but it looks like you heavily pulled from blue already, which works well with Tawil. There are some units that won't be as valuable for new players on the ultra banner, but Jenkin and Winkle work well with Castor.", "timestamp": "2025-10-23T21:07:38.499000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1269527115066507264"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431009422020186142", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431009422020186142", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Pulling and Team Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747088995811358"]}
